"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:2.12\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">2.12</span> 標題：護胸甲（breastplate, chest protector）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： שִׁרְיוֹן</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： shiryan)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:34\">1KI 22:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr18:33\">2CH 18:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:17\">ISA 59:17</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： θώραξ</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： thorax)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:14\">EPH 6:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:8\">1TH 5:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev9:9\">REV 9:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev9:9\">REV 9:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev9:17\">REV 9:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Wis5:18\">WIS 5:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir43:20\">SIR 43:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc3:3\">1MA 3:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc6:2\">1MA 6:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc6:43\">1MA 6:43</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述和用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/OAI-0023_chest_protector_hant.png\" alt=\"護胸甲\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">護胸甲 (Image generated by ChatGPT using OpenAI technology)</figcaption></figure>護胸甲是一件遮護胸部的盔甲（有時也遮護背部），保護胸（背）部不受近戰兵器和弓箭所傷。護胸甲一般是用金屬或用金屬加固的厚皮革製成，遮蓋頸部和腰部之間的胸部，用繫帶繞過背部來固定。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻譯</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:14\">EPH 6:14</a> 和<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:8\">1TH 5:8</a> 中，護胸甲是一個比喻，為要指出一些基督徒美德具有保護的能力（比較<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Wis5:18\">WIS 5:18</a> ）。因此，這種比喻可以譯作：「我們必須用信和愛保護自己，就像穿上盔甲一樣」（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Spanish Common Language Version (Dios Habla Hoy)\">SPCL</abbr> 直譯；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:8\">1TH 5:8</a> b），或「生活正直如你胸膛上的保護」（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Century Version\">NCV</abbr> 直譯；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:14\">EPH 6:14</a> c）。</p>\n<p>在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev9:9\">REV 9:9</a> ，護胸甲是給馬戴的。有時，人們會給戰馬戴上護胸甲來保護牠們免受敵人刀槍的傷害。這節經文的前半節可譯為：「牠們有鱗像鐵製的胸甲」（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> 英文直譯），或「牠們穿著甲胄，好像鐵製的胸甲」（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Jerusalem Bible (1985)\">NJB</abbr> ），或「牠們的身體被一種鐵甲覆蓋」（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Spanish Common Language Version (Dios Habla Hoy)\">SPCL</abbr> ），或「牠們的身體覆蓋著東西，像是保護人胸部的金屬片」。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
